    "name": "Swiftrace Canyon",
    "steam_appid": 2276130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swiftrace Canyon is a high-speed third-person platformer set in an open world canyon inhabited by meerkats. On a hoverbike you complete racing challenges, utilizing a variety of movement mechanics to boost yourself to the top of the leaderboards and unlock new biomes. Beat ghosts of other players by finding unique paths to victory in non-linear races.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced third-person hoverbike platforming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Force mechanics: unique push and pull movement mechanics with a high skill ceiling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 challenge types: mechanical mastery, linear time trial races, and non-linear arena races</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ghost system for an asynchronous multiplayer experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom community leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 biomes: unlockable by completing challenges, each introducing new mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Base movement mechanics: double jump, dash and glide</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 custom drum and bass soundtracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 achievable medals in timed races</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/e817ea30a2ee6e46a18d62a0899a548b.avif?t=1771606900\" width=958 height=166 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FORCE MECHANICS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master unique force mechanics to traverse the world and outpace the competition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/66e9ea1b2e2683ee9f533f09cdad6a3f.poster.avif?t=1771606900\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/66e9ea1b2e2683ee9f533f09cdad6a3f.webm?t=1771606900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/66e9ea1b2e2683ee9f533f09cdad6a3f.mp4?t=1771606900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NON-LINEAR RACING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In arena races you don't have to follow a set path. Come up with your own route to finish a race, find shortcuts and collect all flags as fast as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/10f14bbdae5a623d786901252936e578.poster.avif?t=1771606900\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/10f14bbdae5a623d786901252936e578.webm?t=1771606900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/10f14bbdae5a623d786901252936e578.mp4?t=1771606900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REWIND &amp; RETRY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes things don't go as planned. Rewind your actions and give it another go. You can use this to practice difficult sections of a race.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/0609f2931ab54ed22d3a478dfedd8583.poster.avif?t=1771606900\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/0609f2931ab54ed22d3a478dfedd8583.webm?t=1771606900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/0609f2931ab54ed22d3a478dfedd8583.mp4?t=1771606900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RACE AGAINST GHOSTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select up to 3 ghosts and beat your friends in a head to head race.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/4650285e9422e16e009d2a33f63c0929.poster.avif?t=1771606900\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/4650285e9422e16e009d2a33f63c0929.webm?t=1771606900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276130/extras/4650285e9422e16e009d2a33f63c0929.mp4?t=1771606900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
